Record Class ResumeService

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
services.ResumeService
All Implemented Interfaces:
IResumeService
public record ResumeService(ResumeRepository repository) extends Record implements IResumeService
Service for managing resumes. Implements the IResumeService interface and provides methods to interact with the resume repository.
